Problem

After reviewing the csv data downloaded from the microserver API, these issues have been identified:

timestamps are not correctly formatted

In the microserver data there are 11 date-time variables, from which 10 out of 11 currently do not capture the UTC offset +00:00.

Also, the default missing value for meditation observations in intent_start and intent_finish is “1-01-03T00:00:00”.

session_uuid appears twice

The following session_uuid appears twice:

  • 4e4afec2-7307-424a-86a4-66a6d1d2b45e
  • bbc16d24-0d2e-4f68-8846-da8ec3717ab9
  • 921417b3-c58f-4a80-a8e1-c0381aa81a6a

Although these are not exact duplicates, in the variable type we can see that one is registered as Timer and the other one as < snapshot >. Also points & exp_points don’t match having more points in one of the duplicates. Finally, model_number is a missing value(NA) in one of of the duplicates. It’s important to mention that these sessions are stored in CA server.
